<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>北商財稅系人工選課</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.3.1/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fomantic-ui@2.8.8/dist/semantic.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fomantic-ui@2.8.8/dist/semantic.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="icon" href="images/icon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="/images/banner.png" alt="這是背景圖">
    </div>
    <div class="ui grid two centered">
        <div class="eight wide column">
            <p>助教登入頁</p>
            <p>1.本系統為需要系辦助教核准的課程加退選、減修學分申請需求之用，如欲申請請先登入進行身分驗證。<br> 2.若您欲加退選之課程學校選課系統中仍有名額，則請同學直接登入
                <a href="http://ntcbadm1.ntub.edu.tw/">學校選課系統</a>申請即可，無須登入此系統。<br> 3.申請後不代表已完成，仍須待助教審核後才能確定申請結果，您的申請文件若不齊全則可能有需補件之情形，請同學隨時登入系統查看。
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="four wide column side loginBorder">
            <div class="ui form">
                <div class="field">
                    <label>帳號</label>
                    <input type="text" name="first-name" placeholder="請輸入學號" id="id">
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <label>密碼</label>
                    <input type="text" name="last-name" placeholder="請輸入身份證字號" id="psw">
                </div>
                <button class="ui button" id="login">登入</button>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>




    <script>
        $("#login").click(function() {
            console.log($("#id").val(), $("#psw").val())
            $.ajax({
                url: "./",
                method: "POST",
                data: {
                    "id": $("#id").val(),
                    "psw": $("#psw").val()
                },
                success: res => {
                    res = JSON.parse(res)
                    if (res.success) {
                        $('body')
                            .toast({
                                class: 'success',
                                message: res.message,
                                showProgress: 'bottom',
                                // classProgress: 'red'
                            });
                        localStorage.setItem("token", res.d.token)
                            // console.log(res)
                        document.location.href = "./manage"
                    }
                    // console.log(res)

                }
            })

        })
    </script>
</body>

</html>